{"tid":832943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高鐵通車南行列車隧道內突停駛10分鐘　冷氣燈光熄滅 (11:54)","createTime":"2018-09-23T06:46:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T09:59:06.000Z","uid":41404,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ae94f87e393718d1238ba6027383dea4bb44f192","tid":832943,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T06:46:42.000Z","msg":"造價達844億元的廣深港高鐵香港段今日正式通車。《明報》記者在深圳北站乘坐上午11時02分的復興號列車，返回香港西九龍站，列車駛了約13分鐘時突然減速停駛，窗外漆黑一片，其後車廂的冷氣亦熄滅，部分燈亦關上。<br />\n<br />\n多名乘客其後立即向車務員查詢，有車務員表示不清楚，需了解發生什麼問題。等候約8分鐘後，列車才恢復電力及空調，2分鐘後才再重駛。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180923/s00001/1537674772401\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180923%2Fs00001%2F1537674772401&d=vTi2tvMzgm8sWSCP0n%2FUb5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=8a91bb2c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180923%2Fs00001%2F1537674772401&h=759b823e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180923/s00001/1537674772401</a>"},{"pid":"4c70858b8dc8583da962d0afd1dcd60d9cae9086","tid":832943,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T06:48:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5164809e02a89f03c3566fedbbeb47d1502f69c6","tid":832943,"uid":14244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T06:53:14.000Z","msg":"係地府出返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb9250219222a242f748d495f055006d76e5a4e","tid":832943,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T06:54:45.000Z","msg":"本來係拎d 泥填埋佢<br />\n佢地算大命了, 應該無下次<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\